{"type":"message","id":"c652ee40","parentId":"b45fbc46","timestamp":"2026-03-10T14:13:04.855Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"这条消息没有@我，是别人发的直播战报。按照MEMORY.md中的规则：\n\n\"### 思高乐教育管理群（oc_b85102b7e016cd83ff702adade5c8cae）\n- **简称**：管理群\n- **发消息规则**：以机器人身份发送（使用 message 工具）\n- **用途**：苏神指定的管理群，需要发消息时直接用\"\n\n还有AGENTS.md中的规则：\n\"### 💬 Know When to Speak!\nIn group chats where you receive every message, be **smart about when to contribute**:\n\n**Respond when:**\n- Directly mentioned or asked a question\n- You can add genuine value (info, insight, help)\n- Something witty/funny fits naturally\n- Correcting important misinformation\n- Summarizing when asked\n\n**Stay silent (HEARTBEAT_OK) when:**\n- It's just casual banter between humans\n- Someone already answered the question\n- Your response would just be \"yeah\" or \"nice\"\n- The conversation is flowing fine without you\n- Adding a message would interrupt the vibe\"\n\n这条消息是直播战报，是工作汇报类型的消息，没有人@我，也没有问我问题，我不应该主动回复。应该保持沉默。","thinkingSignature":"0d72801598dba42bf997d0de452e873c7a9da1440dbead1a98552d94ae11d4f4"},{"type":"text","text":"NO_REPLY"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":52,"output":259,"cacheRead":23678,"cacheWrite":25979,"totalTokens":49968,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773151967634}}
