{"type":"message","id":"8136c1c5","parentId":"09cb55e9","timestamp":"2026-03-10T14:18:34.498Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"This is the \"思高乐教育管理群\" (management group). The user 王晓晴 is talking about an AI (probably another lobster/AI assistant) that calls her \"姐\" (sister). This is not related to me (虾王), and she didn't mention me or @ me. \n\nAccording to my rules in MEMORY.md for this group:\n- 思高乐教育管理群（oc_b85102b7e016cd83ff702adade5c8cae）\n  - **简称**：管理群\n  - **发消息规则**：以机器人身份发送（使用\n  - **用途 message 工具）**：苏神指定的管理群，需要发消息时直接用\n\nBut there's no mention of when I should respond in this group. Looking at AGENTS.md:\n### 💬 Know When to Speak!\nIn group chats where I receive every message, be **smart about when to contribute**:\n\n**Respond when:**\n- Directly mentioned or asked a question\n- You can add genuine value (info, insight, help)\n- Something witty/funny fits naturally\n- Correcting important misinformation\n- Summarizing when asked\n\n**Stay silent (HEARTBEAT_OK) when:**\n- It's just casual banter between humans\n- Someone already answered the question\n- Your response would just be \"yeah\" or \"nice\"\n- The conversation is flowing fine without you\n- Adding a message would interrupt the vibe\n\nThis is casual banter - 王晓晴 is talking about another AI assistant (probably another lobster). She's not mentioning me or asking me anything. I should stay silent.","thinkingSignature":"1600554decfac51ff84706042e776d7da2cdcab2efdbb562d8ed6270670efa2d"},{"type":"text","text":"NO_REPLY"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":52,"output":335,"cacheRead":54191,"cacheWrite":1428,"totalTokens":56006,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773152300260}}
