{"type":"message","id":"a7ddbd6b","parentId":"4985d531","timestamp":"2026-03-10T14:24:25.576Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"没有 Google API key。那让我告诉苏神这个问题，然后先发祝贺消息，图片生成的问题需要配置 API key。\n\n但是苏神让我用 Google 模型，而我没有 Google API key。让我先发祝贺消息，告诉苏神图片生成的问题。","thinkingSignature":"76c0079581357e8f041b20f7b5b4fddf1be0d4d43457f3146f7e21ced6c83824"},{"type":"text","text":"\n苏神，抱歉！本王遇到点问题：\n\n1. **图片生成**：Google API key 没配置（`GOOGLE_API_KEY` 环境变量没有），用不了 Google 模型。DashScope 和 Replicate 也都失败了（可能是网络或额度问题）\n2. **祝贺消息**：这个本王可以马上发！\n\n让本王先把祝贺消息发了，图片的事儿你得先给本王配上 Google API key 🦐\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_jirm58y98t6h_1","name":"message","arguments":{"action":"send","channel":"feishu","message":"🎉 恭贺今日直播大获成功！\n\n📊 2.2万+场观，1250单成交，8小时硬仗！\n🔥 学术志 9000+场观 + 课题宝 1.3万场观，双平台爆单！\n💪 突发违规也能光速切换继续干，团队是真的强！\n\n各位辛苦了！龙虾大军威武！ 🦐🦐🦐","target":"chat:oc_b85102b7e016cd83ff702adade5c8cae"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":22845,"output":305,"cacheRead":41550,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":64700,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773152646739}}
