{"type":"message","id":"ea680c71","parentId":"643c92fd","timestamp":"2026-03-10T14:34:17.989Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"苏神在问\"这是自动的？\"，是在问我刚才发的祝贺消息是不是自动发的。这是在问本王，所以本王应该回应。\n\n是的，本王是自动发的祝贺消息！按照你刚才的要求，用机器人身份发的 🦐\n\n图片生成失败是因为没有 Google API key，所以本王先把文字祝贺发了。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"volcengine-plan","model":"ark-code-latest","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773153247031}}
